&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Brief Description of the Role:                                             &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Would you like to join a team that has a reputation for delivering high quality healthcare, where every day is challenging, but rewarding? Then come and see what Bradford Teaching Hospitals Foundation Trust Theatre Teams have to offer.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Rated as “Good” by the CQC, we continually strive for excellence and encourage all members of the team to help influence and drive improvements.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking to recruit full time and part time Band 5 positions across our theatre departments. We have vacancies for Scrub, Anaesthetics and Recovery practitioners. A structured induction package is available to all new starters – preceptorship tailored to professional requirements is offered to all newly qualified nurses and ODPs. We will support you to become the very best that you can be.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a fantastic opportunity for theatre practitioners to enhance, expand and develop their existing skills and knowledge in a diverse range of surgical specialties including Head and Neck surgery, Opthalmology, Trauma and Orthopaedics, Vascular, Breast, Urology, Gynaecology and General Surgery across 19 operating theatres.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for people who share our values. If you believe that you are that person, then please, don’t delay, we would love to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Contact&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Katie Buttery – Team Leader Nucleus Theatres – 01274 364334&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Carol Margerison – Team Leader Modular Theatres– 01274 383052&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Kath Keegan – Team Leader ENT Theatres – 01274 383249&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We can offer staff gymnasiums on both hospital sites, excellent pension scheme and advice on childcare.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Closing Date:                        16.11.20          (This date may change dependent on the response)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
